{"type": "article", "id": 17643, "title": "钢板材料的架子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-17T06:50:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144347J1rmy30ZXtV2bgqf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组钢板材料的架子完全是极简风格，有斜纹遮挡或交叉网格框两种遮挡。前者更适合办公环境，方便归类，也能创造一个有艺术感的环境。后者的网格架可以横放葡萄酒，适合居家环境。因为重量轻，可以随意改变摆放的位置。此外，它的长宽和遮挡类型都是可选的，<a href=\"http://www.teebooks.com/23-etageres-bureau\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144721AiDJW7nuycsjwVgN.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"420\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144721d1vOLzNGCFiDB3tS.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"420\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144722Ob1tsqCgySnmUzMh.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"420\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144722Ky75ZdQ2RYm3znGh.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"420\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}